NUK Baby Bottle Cleanser 950 ml (White)

A natural-based cleaner for tough stains. A babys food in the first few months consists mainly of milk and puree. The tough milk proteins are left in the baby bottle the teat and on the dishes cultivating germs bacteria and bad smells. The NUK BABY BOTTLE CLEANSER has been specially developed for cleaning baby products
